  now available. If you are still having a technical issue with the portal after
  reviewing the FAQ, click on the ‘Request Technical Assistance’ link at the top
  right of the page. Complete the request form and submit. Your issue will be
  communicated and someone from the FirstPic team will reach out within 24 hours
  with a status.

  <br /><br />
  <hr />

